MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

02-140. State v. Scott.

Miami App. No. 2001CA8.

This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and claimed appeal of right. On *1403March 11, 2002, this court ordered appellant to show cause why this appeal should not be dismissed. Whereas appellant has not filed a response to the show cause order,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that his cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
